 selten berührte Themen wie Homosexualität oder die Probleme der Unterschicht werden im vertrauten Briefwechsel erörtert.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 16. Mai 2019) 4aHeyne, Christian G. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aGerlach, Klaus, eeditor.1 aSternke, René, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2015z9783110438673oZDB-23-DKU0 cEPUBz97831103805760 cprintz978305005178940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783050051796423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050051796.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKUb2015